            <title>[FLINK-3339] Checkpointing NPE when using filterWithState</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-3339</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;(1.0-SNAPSHOT)&lt;/p&gt;

